			"value": "<p><em>This set of instruments is used for navigation, often at sea. With navigator's tools, you can chart a ship's course and follow navigation charts, or you can make a map. In addition, these tools give you advantage on any ability check you make to avoid getting lost at sea or try to decipher or use a confusing map.</em></p><p>A @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.SySQiDfSWcSRUCFN]{tool} helps you to do something you couldn't otherwise do, such as craft or repair an item, forge a document, or pick a lock. Proficiency with a tool allows you to use your skills to perform tasks that would be otherwise impossible.</p>",
